WEBVTT

00:46.413 --> 00:49.551
-The Wrath of the Erinys,

00:49.551 --> 00:53.862
punisher of men for crimes
against the natural order,

00:53.862 --> 00:57.413
goddesses of Vengeance
and retribution in Greek

00:57.413 --> 00:59.655
and Roman mythology.

00:59.655 --> 01:03.310
Summoned by victims
seeking justice

01:03.310 --> 01:06.068
pursuers and tormentors
of the wicked

01:06.068 --> 01:08.758
until they atone
for their crimes.

01:08.758 --> 01:11.206
From the blood that spilled on
the earth during

01:11.206 --> 01:13.758
the castration of
the god Uranus,

01:13.758 --> 01:17.068
the Erinys were born.

01:17.068 --> 01:20.344
Megaera the grudging.

01:20.344 --> 01:23.551
Alecto the unceasing.

01:23.551 --> 01:28.793
And Tisiphone,
punisher of murderers.

01:28.793 --> 01:30.724
Gentlemen, I encourage you

01:30.724 --> 01:32.827
to be on your best behavior
around them.

01:34.413 --> 01:37.793
A few reminders before
we start the evening's bidding.

01:37.793 --> 01:40.827
All sales are conducted
in US dollars.

01:40.827 --> 01:42.103
Everything is being sold

01:42.103 --> 01:43.586
according to
the conditions of sale.

01:43.586 --> 01:46.206
And I draw particular attention
to article one,

01:46.206 --> 01:47.655
which states that everything
is sold

01:47.655 --> 01:51.620
under the terms of guaranty
on an as-is basis.

01:51.620 --> 01:53.482
Although the artist is unknown,

01:53.482 --> 01:56.620
the authenticity and period
of the work have been confirmed

01:56.620 --> 02:00.241
by both the Soho Institute
of Fine Arts

02:00.241 --> 02:02.482
and the New York
Preservation Society

02:02.482 --> 02:05.482
and comes with
appropriate certification.

02:05.482 --> 02:09.931
Those who have seen it in our
offices have been entranced

02:09.931 --> 02:11.758
by both the trauma and power

02:11.758 --> 02:15.724
this marvelous
sculpture conveys.

02:15.724 --> 02:21.793
And with that, I'd like to start
the bidding at $50,000.

02:23.413 --> 02:24.620
$55,000.

02:24.620 --> 02:26.034
$60,000.

02:26.034 --> 02:27.137
$65,000.

02:27.137 --> 02:28.689
$70,000.

02:28.689 --> 02:30.413
Are you coming in, Sam?

02:30.413 --> 02:34.241
No? Maybe on the next lot.

02:34.241 --> 02:37.068
$75,000 to Bruce Ernst.

02:37.068 --> 02:39.448
Simon, are you coming in
at $80,000?

02:39.448 --> 02:42.862
I'm at $75,000 now,
and I'm looking for $80,000.

02:42.862 --> 02:45.344
Kate Horna, are you coming in?

02:45.344 --> 02:48.551
Thank you, Kate.
It's your bid at $80,000.

02:48.551 --> 02:52.034
I'm now looking for $85,000.

02:52.034 --> 02:53.689
It's against you, Bruce.

02:53.689 --> 02:56.068
Will you give me $85,000,
please?

02:56.068 --> 02:59.344
Marcel.
Thank you, Marcel.

02:59.344 --> 03:01.965
I'm now looking for $90,000.

03:01.965 --> 03:04.413
Bruce, I would like $90,000.

03:04.413 --> 03:06.275
Could you give me $90,000
please?

03:06.275 --> 03:08.413
Thank you, sir.

03:08.413 --> 03:11.551
Anyone else want to come in
against Bruce's bid?

03:11.551 --> 03:15.068
Alex, are you going
to give me $95,000?

03:15.068 --> 03:18.310
-Bid.
-Thank you, Miss Horna.

03:18.310 --> 03:22.827
$100,000 is now with Marcel.

03:22.827 --> 03:25.172
Bruce?

03:25.172 --> 03:27.206
-You sure?

03:33.275 --> 03:35.655
So you're out, Bruce?

03:35.655 --> 03:38.655
Okay. It's Marcel's bid.

03:40.482 --> 03:42.379
-$105,000.

03:44.586 --> 03:46.413
$120,000.

03:49.620 --> 03:52.793
No? Kate, it's your bid.

03:52.793 --> 03:54.793
-One, two, five.

03:54.793 --> 03:56.793
-$125,000.

03:56.793 --> 03:59.896
The bidding is now with Marcel
at $125,000.

03:59.896 --> 04:01.172
Can I get --

04:01.172 --> 04:03.103
-$130,000.

04:03.965 --> 04:05.655
-No?

04:05.655 --> 04:09.241
Fair warning to the room,
I'm selling to Kate Horna

04:09.241 --> 04:12.000
at $130,000.

04:13.034 --> 04:14.724
There it is.

04:16.551 --> 04:18.655
Thank you, Kate.

04:24.689 --> 04:26.758
-Mm-hmm.

04:26.758 --> 04:29.310
Yeah, of course. Wonderful.

04:29.310 --> 04:31.413
I will bring it back tomorrow.

04:31.413 --> 04:32.793
Okay.

05:12.724 --> 05:14.275
Oh.

05:49.931 --> 05:54.172
Great work, Kate.

06:30.000 --> 06:33.068
-I'm so sorry to bother you.

06:33.068 --> 06:34.379
-What are you doing here?

06:34.379 --> 06:36.275
-I know this is
highly unprofessional.

06:36.275 --> 06:39.000
-Unprofessional?
More like illegal.

06:39.000 --> 06:40.758
What? Did you follow me home?

06:40.758 --> 06:43.413
-Please hear me out, okay?
I'm -- I'm just in town

06:43.413 --> 06:45.896
