$25,000 bonus for you.

07:05.517 --> 07:08.034
-Why?

07:08.034 --> 07:12.586
-Because they see something
beautiful, and they want it.

07:18.068 --> 07:20.068
Your client will literally

07:20.068 --> 07:22.413
double their
investment overnight.

07:28.379 --> 07:31.827
-I'd also like 20%
of your commission.

07:31.827 --> 07:34.206
-Jesus. You play rough.

07:34.206 --> 07:35.551
-You're the one knocking
on my door.

07:35.551 --> 07:39.517
-Yeah, that --
That's fair. Okay.

07:39.517 --> 07:44.931
