the call, and I'll wait outside?

07:44.931 --> 07:48.551
-Don't be an idiot.

07:53.344 --> 07:55.034
-Do you want a glass?

07:55.034 --> 07:56.482
-Oh, that's all right.

07:56.482 --> 07:59.344
