celebrating this, uh, deal.

07:59.344 --> 08:04.068
-Champagne's already open.
Don't be a sore loser.

08:04.068 --> 08:06.862
-So, do you work for a gallery

08:06.862 --> 08:09.551
or a private collector?

08:09.551 --> 08:11.310
-A bit of both.

08:13.103 --> 08:15.689
You have very good taste in art.

08:15.689 --> 08:17.137
-Thank you.

08:17.137 --> 08:21.724
It's a baby collection,
but she's growing.

08:31.689 --> 08:35.000
-Wow.
-Good?

08:35.000 --> 08:36.482
-Very good.

08:38.724 --> 08:41.206
-I'll make the call.

10:47.068 --> 10:50.137
-Stop.

10:50.137 --> 10:52.103
Stop it.

10:52.103 --> 10:53.758
Stop it!

10:55.586 --> 10:57.344
Stop.

11:16.655 --> 11:18.793
-Yeah.

11:18.793 --> 11:22.724
