for a while, but...

11:22.724 --> 11:27.000
that's because he kept
that part of himself hidden.

11:27.000 --> 11:30.206
-Abusive men are
skilled at that.

11:31.344 --> 11:34.068
Has he tried
contacting you again?

11:34.068 --> 11:36.379
-No.

11:36.379 --> 11:38.482
