it's over now.

11:38.482 --> 11:40.827
He'll...

11:40.827 --> 11:45.758
I mean, he knows how to call
the cops if he shows up again.

11:45.758 --> 11:48.275
He learned that lesson
last time.

11:49.620 --> 11:52.344
-And what have you learned,
Meredith?

12:00.620 --> 12:02.689
-I've learned...

12:05.931 --> 12:08.586
...not to absolve a man

12:08.586 --> 12:11.689
for his transgressions
against me.

12:14.517 --> 12:15.827
Bravo.

12:15.827 --> 12:18.344
-Yeah.

12:33.413 --> 12:36.344
-This was quite an undertaking.

12:38.482 --> 12:42.068
What are you so happy about?

12:42.068 --> 12:45.068
-My therapist gave me
a compliment.

12:45.068 --> 12:47.413
-Hey, that's awesome.
-Yeah.

12:47.413 --> 12:48.896
-How's it been going?
-Really good.

12:48.896 --> 12:51.206
Just it feels really nice
to finally feel good

12:51.206 --> 12:53.620
about myself again.
-Yeah.

12:53.620 --> 12:58.482
-His bullshit took up so much
space that I just had to learn

12:58.482 --> 13:00.724
how to not be
defined by it anymore.

13:00.724 --> 13:03.689
-Hey, I'm glad you
stuck with it.

13:03.689 --> 13:05.482
-Thanks.
-Yeah.

13:05.482 --> 13:07.931
We know what a struggle
this last year was for you.

13:07.931 --> 13:09.517
-Yeah.

13:09.517 --> 13:12.275
