being so hot and happy together.

13:22.620 --> 13:25.310
-You're supposed to choose one

13:25.310 --> 13:26.896
and complain about
the choice you make.

13:29.586 --> 13:31.758
-Well, Mer, that just leaves
you and me, so.

13:31.758 --> 13:34.517
-Okay, well, you know that
I love nothing more

13:34.517 --> 13:36.310
than getting drunk
and Googling murders with you.

13:36.310 --> 13:37.655
But I have plans this weekend.

13:37.655 --> 13:39.241
