13:41.068 --> 13:42.896
-I'm getting laid.

13:42.896 --> 13:45.517
Okay. Wait, wait, wait.

13:45.517 --> 13:46.620
-The mystery man.

13:46.620 --> 13:48.172
-Yeah, that's right.
-Mystery man?

13:48.172 --> 13:49.448
