20:39.655 --> 20:40.724
Wow. This is --

20:40.724 --> 20:44.551
-I said it was remote.
Don't worry.

20:44.551 --> 20:47.034
-I'm not worried. It's just --
-What?

20:47.034 --> 20:48.586
-It's dark as hell.

20:48.586 --> 20:52.034
-Well, yeah.

20:52.034 --> 20:54.551
That's just the woods.

20:55.931 --> 20:58.172
-Yeah. No kidding.

21:04.344 --> 21:07.310
-Well, here we are.

21:16.655 --> 21:20.758
This place is really special
to me, Meredith.

21:20.758 --> 21:24.172
Um, it means a lot
that you agreed to come.

21:24.172 --> 21:26.000
-Oh.
-I'm really looking forward

21:26.000 --> 21:28.655
to our time here together.

21:28.655 --> 21:31.172
-It's gorgeous.

21:31.172 --> 21:33.862
-It is, isn't it?

21:33.862 --> 21:37.862
