grab your stuff.

21:37.862 --> 21:39.068
I'll go open her up.

21:39.068 --> 21:41.172
-Uh, okay.

22:26.103 --> 22:29.068
-Leave.

22:29.068 --> 22:31.206
-What?

22:33.655 --> 22:34.896
-Huh?

22:34.896 --> 22:37.413
-That wasn't you?

22:37.413 --> 22:40.758
-I didn't say anything.

22:40.758 --> 22:42.517
-All right.

23:17.482 --> 23:19.310
-Got it.

23:19.310 --> 23:20.655
What are you doing?

23:20.655 --> 23:23.344
Come in. I'll give you
the master tour.

23:50.206 --> 23:52.482
Yeah, I know. It's, uh...

23:52.482 --> 23:55.068
-Oh.
-...rustic.

23:55.068 --> 23:57.931
-Uh...

23:57.931 --> 24:00.758
-No, this is, um...

24:00.758 --> 24:03.448
-It's okay?

24:03.448 --> 24:06.137
-Uh, yeah, it's absolutely
wonderful.

24:07.827 --> 24:09.206
-Yeah?

24:09.206 --> 24:12.068
-Yeah.
Like, I'm actually swooning.

24:12.068 --> 24:13.379
For a cabin.

24:13.379 --> 24:15.965
Yeah, it's just --
it's perfect.

24:15.965 --> 24:18.931
-Good.

24:21.586 --> 24:23.586
Oh, my God.

24:23.586 --> 24:26.068
What?!

24:27.206 --> 24:29.896
-Yeah.

24:29.896 --> 24:31.862
The Wrath of the Erinys.

24:31.862 --> 24:35.068
It's pretty gruesome, isn't it?

24:35.068 --> 24:36.448
I love the drama in it.

24:36.448 --> 24:42.068
I -- I think
they're absolutely terrifying.

24:42.931 --> 24:44.551
-Yeah. Yeah, I know.

