24:58.724 --> 25:00.931
-No.

25:00.931 --> 25:03.482
-Yeah.

25:03.482 --> 25:05.310
Mm-hmm.

25:07.344 --> 25:12.068
-That is a hell
of a reproduction.

25:12.068 --> 25:14.172
-Yeah.

25:16.482 --> 25:20.689
Hey, come on. I'll give you
the rest of the tour.

25:20.689 --> 25:22.448
-All right.

25:27.103 --> 25:32.620
This is where I will be working
my magic this evening.

25:32.620 --> 25:34.448
-I...

25:36.172 --> 25:38.482
I mean...

25:41.310 --> 25:44.620
I'm already enchanted.

25:44.620 --> 25:46.965
-Well, good.

25:46.965 --> 25:49.344
Then I'm ahead of schedule then.

25:51.758 --> 25:54.724
This was going to be
my backup plan.

25:56.068 --> 25:58.034
-Ah.

25:59.275 --> 26:01.827
Okay. Red or white?

26:01.827 --> 26:05.413
-Right now, I'm thinking...

26:07.793 --> 26:08.862
...red.

26:08.862 --> 26:11.758
-Red it is.

26:11.758 --> 26:14.689
-Awesome.

26:14.689 --> 26:17.068
So, any other questions?

26:17.068 --> 26:19.206
-Yes. Where's your bathroom?

28:04.344 --> 28:07.896
-Wow. You look stunning.

28:07.896 --> 28:11.689
To art and beauty.

28:11.689 --> 28:13.965
-And the night ahead.

28:20.551 --> 28:22.482
Um, I brought that record
I was telling you about.

28:22.482 --> 28:24.931
-Oh, great.
Why don't you go put it on?

28:24.931 --> 28:26.379
I'll finish prepping this.

28:26.379 --> 28:28.034
-Yea-- Can I help.

28:28.034 --> 28:31.793
-And spoil the surprise? No.
You go make yourself at home.

30:32.655 --> 30:35.689
-Someone is not
a fan of the past.

31:25.137 --> 31:26.827
-Everything all right?

31:26.827 --> 31:29.482
-Yeah. Yeah. Sorry.

32:11.206 --> 32:14.275
I'm sorry.
I'm not crazy, I swear.

33:34.965 --> 33:37.172
Not yet.

34:10.482 --> 34:13.931
-I'm sorry. Are you okay?

34:13.931 --> 34:15.965
-Yeah. Yeah.

34:15.965 --> 34:19.896
Sorry. I'm just -- I just --
it's the woods or something.

34:19.896 --> 34:21.896
-Oh, you're scared. I...

34:21.896 --> 34:24.137
-No, I'm not. I'm --

34:24.137 --> 34:26.103
-Come inside.
Dinner's ready.

34:26.103 --> 34:28.655
-Okay.

34:49.206 --> 34:53.068
