1:22:26.206 --> 1:22:28.413
-I won't let it.
I won't let it happen again.

1:22:28.413 --> 1:22:30.206
I won't...
-Believe what I say.

1:22:30.206 --> 1:22:33.862
Believe in what I say,
the words that I say.

1:22:33.862 --> 1:22:35.724
-What?!

1:22:35.724 --> 1:22:36.896
What do you want?!

1:22:36.896 --> 1:22:39.000
-The truth in the night.
The words are alive.

1:22:39.000 --> 1:22:40.482
The night is alive.

1:22:40.482 --> 1:22:42.413
-But the day doesn't know.

1:22:42.413 --> 1:22:45.482
-Follow, seek him, round and
round.

1:22:45.482 --> 1:22:49.172
-Scent, snuff, scan the ground,

1:22:49.172 --> 1:22:52.344
lest unharmed he slip away.

1:22:52.344 --> 1:22:59.275
The words that I've said
can't be taken back.

1:22:59.275 --> 1:23:00.793
-What do you want?!

1:23:27.137 --> 1:23:29.241
Of course.

1:23:32.310 --> 1:23:34.793
Oh, this is the perfect place.

1:23:36.896 --> 1:23:39.206
I'm ready.

1:23:39.206 --> 1:23:41.379
I'm ready!

1:23:44.551 --> 1:23:46.172
Where are you?!

1:23:47.827 --> 1:23:49.586
Where...

1:23:56.517 --> 1:23:59.206
Thank you.

1:23:59.206 --> 1:24:01.724
-You don't understand
gratitude, Bruce.

1:24:03.931 --> 1:24:05.586
You're a thief.

1:24:05.586 --> 1:24:10.620
You rob women of their power
and their beauty and their lives

1:24:10.620 --> 1:24:14.551
because you hate that
you have none of those things.

1:24:21.344 --> 1:24:25.965
-I knew you'd understand me.

1:24:25.965 --> 1:24:29.034
You flushed the red owl out.

1:24:29.034 --> 1:24:33.482
You saved us both.

1:24:33.482 --> 1:24:35.793
-It's over.

1:24:35.793 --> 1:24:39.862
-What? No.

1:24:39.862 --> 1:24:42.551
We're just beginning.

1:24:42.551 --> 1:24:47.275
The sun is coming out.
The darkness is gone.

1:24:47.275 --> 1:24:49.413
-I want you to say it.

1:24:53.275 --> 1:24:55.344
-What do you want me to say?

1:24:55.344 --> 1:24:58.827
-"I'm a murderer. I'm a thief."

1:24:58.827 --> 1:25:01.172
-What? No.

1:25:01.172 --> 1:25:03.862
-Admit it.
You're a murderer and a thief.

1:25:03.862 --> 1:25:06.275
-No!

1:25:06.275 --> 1:25:09.413
It was him!

1:25:09.413 --> 1:25:12.586
-Bruce, There's still a lot of
darkness inside you,

1:25:12.586 --> 1:25:14.965
and I can see it.

1:25:14.965 --> 1:25:16.724
It's right there.

1:25:30.724 --> 1:25:33.000
-It's not fair!

1:25:33.000 --> 1:25:35.586
It's not fair!

1:25:35.586 --> 1:25:38.275
Oh. Oh!

1:25:42.896 --> 1:25:44.413
Cut him off, please!

1:25:44.413 --> 1:25:47.448
-Say it! "I'm a murderer.
I'm a thief."

1:25:47.448 --> 1:25:49.827
-Cut him off! Cut him off!

1:25:49.827 --> 1:25:52.068
It's not who I am!

1:25:52.068 --> 1:25:55.000
No! Ah!
No!

1:25:55.000 --> 1:25:59.793
Cut him off, please!
Ah!

1:25:59.793 --> 1:26:01.310
Promise...

1:26:01.310 --> 1:26:04.724
Cut him off, please!

1:26:07.620 --> 1:26:09.827
Please!

1:26:09.827 --> 1:26:11.206
No, God!

1:26:11.206 --> 1:26:13.724
Cut him off, pl--

1:26:24.206 --> 1:26:25.965
Please!

1:26:25.965 --> 1:26:29.379
Please, help me!

1:26:29.379 --> 1:26:30.689
Meredith!

1:26:30.689 --> 1:26:32.551
-Go fuck yourself.

1:26:46.724 --> 1:26:50.413
-Meredith!
